00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,730
to get the Xuantian Teachings.

854
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,120
And to see what he's

855
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:08,930
really up to.

856
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:10,980
What about Ranran?

857
00:41:27,350 --> 00:41:29,250
[Two days later]

858
00:41:49,030 --> 00:41:50,590
She will have her own life,

859
00:41:51,920 --> 00:41:52,780
a brand new life

860
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:55,440
without me.

861
00:42:25,280 --> 00:42:25,800
Ranran,

862
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:30,840
I bear much responsibility for your reincarnation,

863
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:33,570
which is why I brought you back to the Wester Sect.

864
00:42:35,700 --> 00:42:37,990
Now, all our past favors and grudges are dissolved.

865
00:42:37,990 --> 00:42:38,970
And I have more important things

866
00:42:38,970 --> 00:42:39,900
to attend to now.

867
00:42:42,630 --> 00:42:43,960
I won't come back again.

868
00:42:45,030 --> 00:42:46,630
You should leave on your own.

869
00:42:53,630 --> 00:42:55,690
If you still consider me your master,

870
00:42:56,480 --> 00:42:57,190
promise me

871
00:42:58,360 --> 00:43:00,290
you won't be held back by anything.

872
00:43:01,630 --> 00:43:02,960
Live as freely as the wind.

